Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , Eroodɛ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a Galile a ̀ woka ̀ di ɓɛɛ ɓu ̀ ŋɓuŋ Yeesus , a ̀ ki kpaa ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ :
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ remza ̀ ka ̀ ri ̀ si ̀ tam ̀ ; ɓi mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m mɛ a Isirayɛl , ɓum ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m mɛ ̀ tin taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛnin .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki n ̀ kpaa ki yin lɛ , ɓi ɓa lɛ i ɓi ̀ ghɛɓsii ɓum ɓɛɗɛŋ mi ̀ nii rɔɓ ri ̀ ki ̀ sogha ̀ ; ki ri lɔŋ kiɓan ki lɛ ɓi ghɛɛ ̀ sag ;
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ dɔgtɛ ̀ n i ̀ Pol , ɓɛ toosi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ zɛy lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛyiti ̀ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓis ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ i nfaa ɓi ̀ si i ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓi nyoo ri ̀ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗin , ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛce ̀ m mɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɔ .
Lɔŋ wɔɔ foo , ŋwaa ̀ -fi ̀ tom a Kan a ̀ ɓog nyi ɓisuulɛ a ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓum ɓɛɛ fa nyi ri ̀ kem ɗi ɗi ghɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ fa Bɛ ̀ ll . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛgɛn ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi ri ̀ ɗiɗi ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ wu .
Kan a ̀ ɓa ̀ g Maata lɛ : Maata wɔ ̀ , u kpuukputɛ ̀ n , nɗem wɔɔ wu ki cɛɛcɛɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ghɛn di Moyis ri ̀ Eli ɓɛ ti ɓii ̀ to ̀ toogh ri ̀ nyi .
Fɔɔnnɛ Ɓarinaɓas a ̀ teka ̀ Sol a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ nyi a ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ yɛ ̀ ɛ Sol a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ Kan ɓi bee i ̀ nɛ a Damas ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kan a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi , nni a ̀ kpaati ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ kuu ɗi n ̀ tyweeyi ɗi Sol a ̀ a n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ a Damas di a kakali ɓum ɗii ɗi Yeesus .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ fɔɔ ̀ fɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ sɛ ̀ n mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ mɛrem ri ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ .
Ɓi nka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ nyi , a ̀ teka ̀ ɓi nyoey lɛ a tuu ̀ zi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗi fati ̀ gha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki fa Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ɗem wu Yeesus wu nyɛŋɗɛ ̀ nga ̀ ti ̀ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a zɔ ̀ ŋ . Zɔ ̀ ŋ i ̀ nce ̀ m i ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ tuɓɛn ɓi gɔ ̀ g ɓɛ simi ̀ gɔ ̀ g i ̀ dɛŋ a ŋwɔm .
Fɔɔnnɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri Yeesus , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a ̀ regi ̀ gha ̀ Lazaari lɛ a kpaŋ yi ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ , a ̀ ghe ̀ mzi ̀ nyi , i ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ kin ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ sii ̀ ɓɔmɓɔm lɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ pɛs ɓisi ɓi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ si ̀ ɗi ɓyoo mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni ɓi ntɛ ̀ g wu mii ̀ wu seesee ɓi ̀ si .
Ɓi ki ̀ ki ɓidaŋa ̀ ɓi zɛy ! ɓi ̀ yii ɓi lɛ maa nwi ̀ ɗ lɛsa ̀ g a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g n ̀ ku ̀ ŋ wu ɓɛ tɔɓi ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm , nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ a ̀ nɛn ri ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay a ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ ka ̀ nyi , lɛ nyi ɓa ɓi nɗaŋ waanɛ ̀ n .
Roa ̀ nɛ a kalag lɛ ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ri saaɗ a kpaaghi lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ! Mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ̀ yu ̀ yuiy lɔɔ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki . A ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ! Yuiy ɓa ̀ , Kan Yeesus !
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : U ̀ gherɛɛ ɓisuulɛ u ̀ mɛ ghɛn mɛ ? Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛn .
Lɛ a kalag lɛ : M ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi syeesyee a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ; n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ gha ̀ wɔ ̀ ŋwosi go ̀ ri . Syeesyee a ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n innɛ min lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , ŋwosi go ̀ ri innɛ min lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ki ki cee kɛɛ ri lɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ gwey a ̀ nɛ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi wee ̀ lem a ̀ ri ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓi ɗyoo ɓi ɗu ̀ m ,
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi naa , a ̀ reɓ ɓɔ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛɛ la ̀ y ; ɓi duri tana nnɛ ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ kɛn ̀ . Ɓɛ ̀ ge ̀ ni ɓii ɓɛ righerɛ ̀ n ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ a Zyope ɓɛ kɛn ̀ ga ̀ nyi ki ̀ foŋi ̀ .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n , ɗii lɛ Kirispus ɗi gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Kan , ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii ɗice ̀ m , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓumɓɛ a Kɔrɛŋt lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Pol ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ girig , ɓɛ ki ɓa ̀ ɓtag .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ mɛɛ mii , a ̀ reɓsa ̀ g ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓii ri ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say lɛ , ri ̀ a ̀ nɛn mii ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ su wii wu kisay , a ̀ ki siitag m ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -i ̀ suunaa lɛ , a kɔri cem .
Com ki mi ̀ nii ghɛɛ lɛ ki ri lɛ syeesyee , ki ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓaa ̀ com ki kɛɛ ki lɛ ɓi totog ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin kiɓe mii ̀ .
Nni fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ woka ̀ di jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ i ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Mi ̀ ni ɓɔn ɓɛm , pɛ ̀ sɛɛna ɓi ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛn , di kɛ ̀ ɓi teɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ki ̀ ɓe ki yɔ ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ ɓya ̀ a ɓa ɓi ri ga ̀ ɓ ɓi mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ yɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ kɛ ̀ ɓi risi com , lɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ ɓi mi ̀ ni ɗi cee com ki ɓɛ ̀ fyas lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ri lɛ ɓɛ tɔn .
Ki ̀ rɔɔ kaa ki te ̀ ghɛɛ bee lɛɛ ̀ gwey ; ri ̀ ɓɔ nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ka loka ̀ ki ̀ reɓsɛɛ ɓiɓan ɓii .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓii lɛ : Man win ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi kpaaghi lɛ a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ti ̀ ɗyaŋ yɛɛ ri lɛ ? Nni lannɛ a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ghɛnɛɛghɛnɛ ̀ n ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ i ɓya ̀ a wog rikɛŋ ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ geesɛ ̀ n bimiɗ , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ reŋi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi teɗ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗi fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ konagh ki rɛsii lɛ syeesyee nyimiɗ , a ̀ si ̀ i ̀ ra ̀ g mi ̀ ni , a ̀ fa mi ̀ ni i ̀ te ̀ ɗ , a ̀ ki ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓa ɓumɓɛ com ki yin lɛ ki ɓigti ̀ .
a ̀ rɔɓ lɛ a ̀ fɔ ̀ ni ɓi a ̀ cee le ̀ g a ̀ nɛn ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , a ̀ ki fɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ di cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛ mɛ rii ̀ , a ̀ yin .
lɛ di gasɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa ɓi nyoo i ̀ mum , ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ɓ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ ɗi za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓyɛɛ ɓee ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n ɓyɔ ri ̀ ɓyɔ .
