Fɔɔnnɛ Ananyas a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ min wɔɔ ; nni yɛɛ ̀ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa i ̀ nɛ Sol a ̀ ɓagha ̀ mii ̀ , a ̀ saagh nyi ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo a ki kpaa nyi lɛ : Geni wɛ ̀ m Sol , Kan Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ɗe ̀ sɛɛ yi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓi bee di u yu ̀ yuiy fɛ , yɛɛ romii ̀ mɛ ̀ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , lɛ mɛ ̀ nsaagh wɔ ̀ ɓya ̀ g ɓi nyoo di wɔ ̀ ɔ ghɛnɛn ti ̀ , u ̀ ki ɓa nɗonɛn ɗi Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay .
Mi ̀ nii ɓɔɔghna ɓi kɛn ̀ ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ , ɓi san wɛ ̀ m , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka yin ɓii ̀ ɓɔɓɔɔgh wɔɔ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɛm ̀ ki ka ghɛɛ ̀ sɛn ɓi .
A ̀ fe ̀ fe ̀ ka ̀ ɓi nɗem wii lɛ : I m ̀ ma ̀ nɛɛ ki ̀ ko ̀ mi nsoo ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ a ̀ kii , di n ̀ wɔ ̀ ni .
E ̀ e e ̀ e ki ̀ cu ̀ ma ̀ ki bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ lɛ Mɔlɔg ri ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki fyɛy fi bɛ ̀ ll yi ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Refan ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ tɛ ̀ ka ̀ , ɓi ̀ syag ɓi ̀ nu ̀ n ɓin ̀ lɛ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ gsi ̀ ; ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki naŋi ̀ fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , Baɓilon a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ fɛ ajɛ ̀ m .
Ɓi do ̀ o ̀ yi Davit a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ Yeesus a yalɛn fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ghɛɓsi ̀ lsrayɛl , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ nyimiɗ a ka ̀ ka ̀ .
I ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n a ̀ giɓ a ri ̀ ri ̀ yii a ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin ngherɛ ̀ n , yii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki gherɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ kɛn ̀ asu ɓɛ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓ naa bog , giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki ɓe ̀ ni yii a ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Foo n ̀ la ̀ nag wu yii ̀ di ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ muu Gi ̀ rɛg , ri ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛn , ri ̀ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin nkɛ ̀ rɛn , n ̀ ke ̀ n a mum , ri ̀ muu Sit , nsoo ̀ lɛ ri ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ yin n ̀ kpa ̀ n , lɔŋ Kiris yɛɛ ri com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a zɔ ̀ ŋ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ tɛka ̀ zɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ghɛn lɔŋ zyo ̀ na ̀ yi ɓila ̀ a ̀ yɔri ̀ yɔ ɓi zi . Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y a mɛɛ di a kuukuu ̀ ghra ̀ g ki ̀ ɓan ki ki kilɛ ̀ nga ̀ kin ̀ .
Ti ̀ i n ̀ woogh di a kpaakpaa lɛ , a ɓii ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ ghii naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ toga ̀ i ̀ nɛ , a ̀ toŋdi ̀ i ̀ dɛŋ ɓi mɛ ̀ ru mɛraa mum kɛ ̀ ɛ foŋ ca ̀ g mii ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ , a ̀ tumɛn ri ̀ la ̀ a ̀ la ̀ mɓɛ ̀ n ɗi com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki Yeesus a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓisu wii ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ɓɛ nɗegi lɛ , ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki ba ̀ n n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ . Ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ kuura ̀ ka ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ nga ̀ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɓi bim inɛ n ̀ woka ̀ , n ̀ kpaa lɛ : Ɓaa ɗiŋi ɓi ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ m ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ri fɔɔsɛn wɔɔ , nsoo ̀ ŋwos .
Ma ̀ ŋina ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ cɛmgi ̀ mi ̀ ni , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋza ̀ g ɓisuu ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ tɔtɔɓ mini .
Jɛɛ gili Simɔn a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ nɔ ̀ ŋnɔ ̀ ŋ lɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ tɔ ̀ gtɔ ̀ g . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ fyɛɗmɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ Yeesus fi ̀ roɓ fi giɓ anɛ ̀ n .
a ̀ tɔkii yi ̀ wɔ ̀ , Marikus ri ̀ Aristarikɛ ri ̀ Demas , ri ̀ Lukas ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ reŋka ̀ ŋ ɓɛm ɓɛ kisay ɓɛ togsaagh yi ̀ girig wɔ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghaasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ɓi n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ , ɓi ɗu ̀ m , lɛ di a wog ɓɔ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ i nɗi ̀ ri ̀ nyi cɛcɛɗ ki Zyuridɛŋ , a ̀ nɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ntɛɛzsii ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ ɓa ɗii , a ̀ ti girig ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ aɓaɓti ̀ ɓum , fɔɔnnɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛɛ ̀ su ̀ usuu ̀ rɛ ̀ n a lɔ ̀ ŋkii .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ɓi mɛɛ aɗyoo , kɛɛ ̀ sɛɛdii lɛ a teɗ com ɓi na ̀ a ̀ .
Nnyɛɛ ri N ̀ ghay a ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ ɓiɓan a ̀ nɛ ziinɛ i ̀ yin lɛ i ̀ teɗ , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ ghɛɛ ɓi nyi , yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki yi nyi . Lɔŋ mi ̀ ni yɛɛ yii nyi ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ni .
Yeesus a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ n ɓi ba ̀ n , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ lali ̀ a Bɛtanii .
Ki ̀ du ̀ ŋdu ̀ ŋ ki mum ki ! Com ki u ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li ki yin lɛ ki ghɛɓ di ki wii ɓi ̀ !
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : N ̀ kalii ɓi wɔ lɛ lɔŋ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ; n ̀ kalii wɔ ̀ lɛ ; gɛ ̀ n mɛtin mɛraa ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ a ̀ kpaŋ , fɔlɔɔ gɛ ̀ n taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ gasɛ ̀ n i ̀ yin ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ muu Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n , ri ̀ muu Gi ̀ rɛg , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ri lɔŋ Kan bog a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ fala ̀ g ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ rereŋi nyi ɓyom .
Nsoo ̀ gi ̀ lɛ di ti faa ̀ fa ̀ lɛ ̀ n i ̀ te ̀ ɗ nɗaŋ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri ɓi ̀ si bas lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni .
ki ̀ ɓan kifog i ɓɛ ɓɛli yɔ ̀ , i ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ , i ̀ tɔɔ , i ̀ ghay coo kite ki ki ceghii ɓi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ li ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi dɛm , ki foŋ ɓyoo myaɓ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ti ̀ i ̀ li ̀ ti aɗyoo ti ri lɛ ti togi ̀ ɓi ̀ laa ɓyaa mii ̀ .
Nni Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ taŋzɛ ̀ nga ̀ di ɓɛ mɛ wog lɛ , Yeesus a ̀ a si ̀ mi Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ŋwɔm .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus ɓɛ sugtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɛɛ Zyayirus , coo kituu ki ɓum ki nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ nyi , ki kɔm ̀ nyi , ki ki si ̀ isii ̀ ri ̀ nyi .
Ta ̀ a ̀ ta , kemzi ɗii ɗyɔɔ . Nni jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ y aɗyoo lɛ : M ̀ mɛ kemzi ɗyɔ , m ̀ ɓii ̀ ki kemzii ti ɗyɔ ̀ .
Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki nɔ mɛrɔ ̀ g , mi ̀ ni lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ghay .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓɔ girig ɓɛ mɛ re ̀ si n ̀ too ̀ te ̀ ɗ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , lɛ di Bɛ ̀ ll a wog ɓɔ girig nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a ncenɛɛ mi ̀ ni .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ re ̀ nɗeni gɛ , ɓi ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ di ̀ min , di ɓya ̀ a ghɛn lɛ ri ̀ Abiraham , ri ̀ Isag , ri ̀ Yakɔɓ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ki tyɔg mini ɓi dan .
Ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kana ̀ g bɛ ̀ ɗ ri mii mɛ ɓɛroɓɛ ɓɛ ceetii ɓɔ ; ri ̀ ka ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɗi bɛ ̀ ɗ ɗyɛɛti ɗi rengi ̀ nywey ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛɛ ̀ nyoonyolɛ ̀ n .
Tyɛ ̀ ki fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn Kan fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wa ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ feeghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi , ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ cuugha ̀ di nyoo yi taɓkii ɓɔ .
I ŋwaa ̀ gha ̀ ɓi n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɗii ɗi lɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ti ɓɛ teki ̀ ; nni ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki gha ̀ ɓi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ mɛ ̀ le ̀ ɓ mɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛɛ ̀ teki ̀ .
A ̀ romi gɛ ɓum ɓii ɓɛ titom ri ̀ ɗyam ɗigwey , ɓi mɛ ̀ fon mɛ zi mɛnin , lɛ ɓɛɛ taŋzɛn ɓum ɓii ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ nɛn ɓi zi bimiɗ ri ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ tum ɓɛ zi ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Filiɓ a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : I u ̀ gherɛɛ ri ̀ n ̀ ɗem wɔɔ wuce ̀ m n ̀ ɗi lɛ m ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ wɔ ̀ ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , n ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ Yeesus Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Nni a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ foo a ̀ kɛ ̀ n a mɛɛ mɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ɗisa ̀ g Bɛ ̀ ll ɗii lɛ Tityus-Yustus , mɛɛ mii mɛ ɓagha ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ naa ̀ -bɔ ̀ ŋzɛ ̀ n .
I ŋwaa ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ku ̀ na , di a ̀ ka ̀ nɛɛ bɛ ̀ ɗ yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ku ̀ na ɗyɔmiɗ , ri ̀ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ki sasaghii mii ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ɓɔgsa ̀ g lɛ ri ̀ go ̀ n yidɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛdɛŋ , ri ̀ ɓya ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓidɛŋ ri ̀ be ̀ g yidɛŋ .
U ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa bimiɗ a ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , ɓɛ ɓa ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll , ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ la ̀ mii ziinɛ .
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ pɛ ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ kpaa Yeesus lɛ : Raɓi ̀ , ki ri ki ̀ rɔɔ di ti ̀ kɔ ̀ rii fɛ ̀ , ti ̀ toŋ ɓi ̀ laa ɓiraa lɛ , kifog ɓisu wɔɔ , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Moyis , ki ̀ fog ɓisuu Eli .
Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɗii nyoo yɛ ̀ m , a ̀ ki nɔ bwaɓ yɛm ̀ , a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ghe ̀ mzii nyi ɓi siito ̀ n a ŋwos .
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ -yii syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ nyi , innɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ti n ̀ saa ̀ sa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓumɓɛ a Masedwan ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , di nkpaakpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ a Akayi ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ pe ̀ gsɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ghɛɓsi a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi be ̀ g i ̀ mbog . Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗin ɗi nfatii ɓi ̀ seŋi lɛɛ ̀ gwey ite ̀ ɗ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
I mum a ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ ki ri n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ lɛ gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ yɛɛ ghay i ̀ cee gba ̀ a ̀ i ̀ nɛ giɓ a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ mii ̀ ki ̀ wɔlɛɛ , nni a ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ yɔ ̀ ki faa ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wɛy , a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i com ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ; fɔlɔɔ a yin kiɓe ; ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wɔlɛɛ .
Nni wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki , n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ a Yorisalɛm ɓisuu fitom fi fi seesee ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓɛ wɔɔ .
