Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis a ̀ peegha ̀ y ɓi-reɓ wu a Zyude , a ̀ kaka ̀ li ̀ ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll .
Abiraham a ̀ ɓa ̀ gti ̀ nyi lɛ : I ɓɛ ̀ goni ɓɛ yin lɛ ɓɛ wog ri ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɗi Moyis ri ̀ ɗi ɓɛkpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , nsoo ̀ mum a ̀ a ghe ̀ mɓɛɛ yi ̀ fɛ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɓɔ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ ki ̀ ɓan , ɓaa gherɛn ɓi .
Ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɗimzɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ teɗ ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , lɔŋ bi ̀ rɛs bog yɛ ̀ ɛnɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ ɓi ki ̀ kɔm .
I ti ̀ ki yii lɛ , a wowog ɓisi , nsoo ̀ cɛ kɛɛ ̀ ki tya ̀ a lɔni nyi , ti ̀ yi lɛ , ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ com ki ̀ n mii ̀ .
Kan Yeesus a ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y a ̀ pɛɓsɛ ̀ n Pyɛɛri Fɔɔnnɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ yiti ̀ gha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ Kan Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ nyi lɛ : N ̀ lem a ̀ zag a ri ̀ ɓii ̀ rɔŋi ̀ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ di u ̀ mɛ roo ̀ zɛn mɛ gɛ ̀ n yiraa .
