Lɔŋ m ̀ bobog a ̀ Nghay a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓiɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ka ̀ aka ̀ ɓsi ̀ ɓyɔ lɛ ri ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n mii ̀ a ̀ fa com ki a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni .
N ̀ -yin ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa kiɓan kin ̀ lɛ nfa mi ̀ ni bɛ ̀ lɛn . Lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ma ̀ a kpaa mini , ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ ɓisi ɓi nɗem nsoo ̀ ɓi cɛɓ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wu .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ a ̀ suka ̀ , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ n ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn ɓi ɓyomɓilɔ ̀ ŋ , ɗi ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki n ̀ ghay ki mɛ pɛ ̀ sɛn yɔ ̀ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Nni lannɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki kpaakpaa di ɓɛ romi ɓi nyi ? Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : Ki rɔɔtɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ lɛ u ghɛn ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ rii ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ syeesyee ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ ɓɔlɛ di ɓɛɛ yu ̀ yuiy .
Ri ̀ lema ̀ g ɗyɔmiɗ ɗi ti ̀ ti ti ̀ kemza ̀ g Kan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Seŋi wi ̀ s ri ɗyɔ , ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ti ̀ ti ti ̀ nyɔ ̀ ma ̀ g ɓumɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ki ̀ pisɛn kii ri ɗyɔ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn ɓi ki ̀ to ̀ n ki n ̀ lɛmɓog , nni giɓ adɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n-ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ yugha ̀ y ,
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ , fyɛɛ ̀ fyɛɛ ̀ ɓi ŋwɔm i ̀ ghe ̀ y ɓi ɗu ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ fala ̀ g ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ki ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ i ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓyom ɓi ɓi dɛm fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ zo ̀ o ̀ ri ̀ ba ̀ a ̀ zi ̀ , ri ̀ ge ̀ g , ɓi ̀ sɛɛti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ lem ɓɛ ɓiɓan ɓɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓɛ ɓɛ ri lɛ : ri ̀ saaɗ , ri ̀ nɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ɗi ̀ ri ̀ roo ̀ zi ̀ ɗi mɛka ̀ g , kɔm ̀ lɛ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ̀ n ̀ ɓyɛɛ ̀ ɓi mum a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i , kɛ ̀ ɛ ki sɛɛti ɓimbog .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ tɔtɔ ̀ ka ̀ ɓum ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ pon , roa ̀ nɛ , ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛtan ̀ , roa ̀ mbog , dola ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ .
N-yiiyiti ̀ girig ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ ghe ̀ y azi ɗi ɗi ri wɔ ̀ ɓi nɗem , ri ̀ kuu ɗi righerɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi gaa a ̀ n ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn anɛ lɛ Lɔyis a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyɔ , Enis a ̀ jɛɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ri ɗyɔ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗem wɛ ̀ m wu ̀ ce ̀ m wu gherɛɛ lɛ ɗi ri girig fɔlɔɔ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ .
Syeesyee a ̀ ki ̀ te bimiɗ a ̀ ti a ̀ wumgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi syeesyee ; ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kite ki wumgi ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɗu ̀ n .
Nni yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ri ̀ lɛ yaɓi ̀ yaɓi ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ke ̀ ŋmɛn , kɔ ̀ ɔ ki tɔ ̀ n , n ̀ ɗi ̀ wɔ ̀ ɓii ̀ loghii a ŋwɔm .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g nyi lɛ : Mum a ̀ yin lɛ a ̀ ghɛɓ lɛ bi ̀ rɛs yɔ ̀ ri yɔ ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ a ɓisu wii cɛ ̀ ncii nnɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ , ɓɛ ghɛnga ̀ nyi lɛ saaɗ a ̀ mum ɓisuu kiɓan kin ̀ .
Nni man a ̀ n ̀ kpa ̀ n a giɓ anɛ ̀ n , a ̀ yalɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɔn ɓɛ ti ɓɛ yala ̀ g , wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ man a ̀ giɓ anɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓi n ̀ kpa ̀ n nyii yalɛɛ , ri ̀ yalɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ɓagha ̀ y ɓi nka ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ nyi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu lɛ a lami ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ fa ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ nyi cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Ɓigomi ̀ nɛ n ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romga ̀ y mɛ ̀ . Nsoo ̀ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ u ̀ tɔɔgh ɓi mɛ lɛ , u ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ fe ?
Nni Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ nyi lɛ : Kan , i ki ri saaɗ lɛ , wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri , gherɛn lɛ , nkɛɛ ̀ ghii ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ nig , n-yu wɔ ̀ a nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Simɔn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ caka ̀ g ri ̀ ki ̀ lo ̀ ŋ kii , ri ̀ Zyudas Iskariyot , ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ka ̀ ɓka ̀ Yeesus .
Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ lamɓa ̀ a ̀ nɛ a ro ̀ o ̀ ro ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpee ̀ kpe ̀ ŋzi ̀ ja ̀ ŋ , nni ki kɔnga ̀ mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi nyaa ̀ rɛn ri ̀ ki ̀ tɛɛtɛn kii ɓi maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n .
ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ a nkɔ ̀ ni lɛ a resi ɓɔ fe ̀ g wi ̀ i ̀ anɛ a ri ̀ nyam , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ , a ̀ fɔm a ̀ ki rɔɔtɛn yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ; fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛn a ̀ ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi yii ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll , nnyɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ : Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mi ̀ ni , a ̀ ki fa mini dya ̀ ɓɛn inɛ lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ ɓi ri ̀ kem ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll .
I ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , Kiris a ̀ ri ̀ fɛ nsoo ̀ lɛ fɛnii , kɛ ̀ ɓi wog ;
Ki ghɛɓsii ɓi com lɛ nkan ̀ yi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ki seesee gɛɓsɛ ̀ n i ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔkɔnɛ ̀ n ɓisuu ɓɛgherɛ ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nti mɛ ̀ yɛɛ ɓɔnga ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ntɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ? N ̀ soo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki ̀ bog ki ɓi mi ̀ ni ki ri Sata ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ , n ̀ ghɛn ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ to ̀ to ̀ ka ̀ a ̀ nɛn ri ̀ mɛ ̀ . Yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ nni n ̀ ghɛnga ̀ ɓyom ɓi ɓɛɛ ̀ rɛsag lamɓa ̀ mii ̀ taa ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki ̀ yɛn ɗi gol .
