Mɛ ̀ n-yii fe ̀ g a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ri ̀ nyam fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ma ̀ a fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛɛ mi ̀ ni ki ̀ co ̀ ŋi lɛsa ̀ g lɛ nnyɛɛ resii mɛ ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛn .
a ̀ yɛ ̀ gsi ̀ nyi ɓya ̀ g , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Kan ! n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wɛm ̀ a nɔ ̀ nɔŋii a mɛɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ bee inɛ lɛ a pɛsɛn aɗyo ̀ o ̀ ; a ki wowog rikɛŋ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
Fɔɔnnɛ man a ̀ nɛn a tɔɔtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ gha ̀ a ̀ ki te ̀ etee ̀ sɛ ̀ n ; a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n lɛɛ ̀ gwey , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki keekee ̀ si ̀ nyi .
Ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ mɛ wog ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , nni ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ lɛ : Ki ri lɔŋ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ yɛɛ ri n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ i ɓɛ m ̀ pisii myaɓ mɛ o ̀ livyee mɛdɛŋ , wa ̀ a ̀ nɛ u ̀ ri ̀ ( fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ) o ̀ li ̀ vyee a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛghɛ ̀ ɓka ̀ ɓi cog , u ̀ ɓa lɛ ɓɛ yuu ̀ wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ɓaatii ɓi nɗye ̀ m wu o ̀ livyee , ja ̀ ŋ inɛ myaɓ mɛ ɓɛ nɗengii mɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ , u teteɗ girig ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ mɛ ̀ yaa mɛ ga ̀ ŋ yi o ̀ livyee a ̀ nɛ ɓɛ ɓɛla ̀ yɛɛ ̀ ronɗom ̀ yi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kifog kɛɛ ri ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n ; Marii a ̀ a ɓɔ ̀ ni ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ syeesyee ; ɓaa ɓa ̀ tɛn ɓi nyi yɔ ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ , mɛ ̀ ru mɛdɛŋ mɛ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ , mɛɛ ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ɓii ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔg , ma ̀ a ̀ gh ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɓɛ ɓɛ ka yala ̀ ɓi , ri ̀ ɓɛ ɓɛ ka nyɔŋzi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi man .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ te ̀ e ̀ sii ɓya ̀ g ɓin ɓi ɓyaa nyɔŋi ̀ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ɗu min mɛ maa kpɔ ̀ gti ̀ .
Yeesus a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo , a ̀ maasi ̀ .
Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Zyanɛs ri ̀ Zyamɓirɛs ɓɛ ramga ̀ wɛ ̀ y ri Moyis , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓumɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛɛ ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu girig ri ̀ saaɗ , ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ nghay waa wu ti wu ̀ ɗimɛn bee , ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗyaa ɗi yin ̀ lɛ ɗi ɓanɛ ̀ n di mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mɛ tanɛɛ ɓɔ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓisu waa , yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ ɓenga ̀ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ lɛ Zyaŋ a ɓaɓti ɓɔ .
M ̀ ɓi ̀ i ̀ tii ki ̀ kpaa ̀ lɛ : mum kɛ ̀ ɛ teɗ mɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , nko ̀ o lɛ , ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , gha ̀ ɓina mɛ ̀ ɓi si ̀ g a ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , di fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nki girig maa kalɛn lɛsa ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pyɛɛri a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ka to ̀ tog fɔlɔɔ nni coo kikwi ̀ ɗ ki lo ̀ nlomɛn ki si ̀ gtɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ . Fɔɔnnɛ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓi ki ̀ kwi ̀ ɗ kin ̀ , i ̀ kpaa lɛ : Roa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ Man wɛm ̀ a ̀ nɗem , ɓi nyi innɛ n ̀ foga ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n wɛ ̀ m bimiɗ , wooghna nyi .
Nkpaaghi lɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri ɓi ̀ si n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ ; ki pisɛɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ i nɗe ̀ sii lɛ ti ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ kɔ ̀ g , ɓi ri ̀ ca ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗin ̀ , nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki ̀ ɓan kice ̀ m ki mum a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ , mɛ ̀ girig n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ ki ̀ kpaa ̀ kɔ ; nto ̀ tog yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g .
Yeesus a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki ɓi ɓɔ ̀ ɔɓɔŋza ̀ g , kaliina lɛ : Ta ̀ a ̀ ta ! Ɗii ɗyɔɔ ɗyɛɛ ɓa ɗi ̀ tɛnɛn ; ki ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ kɔɔ kɛɛ yu .
Ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , kaaza a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ Ogus , a ̀ lami ̀ gha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓay ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓi zi bimiɗ .
Dyaaki ̀ rɛ ̀ a ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓaa ̀ giɓ bog , a ̀ ki kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , ri ̀ ri ̀ mɛɛ ɗii lɛ syeesyee .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ɓa ̀ ka ̀ ɓi com ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ɓɛgwey ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn ɓɛ kpaagha ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ rara ̀ ɗ ri ̀ nyi .
Ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓin ɓɛ togsaagh yi ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛce ̀ m ; to ̀ oto ̀ gsɛɛna mi ̀ ni ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ lɔ ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɓi nkɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ geni .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ɓi riɓa ̀ y ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ghɛŋɗa ̀ ka ̀ , do ̀ n yɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ghɛnɛn ti nsoo ̀ bog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛghay ɓi ̀ n ɓi ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzi ̀ gha ̀ Yeesus lɛ , kɛ ̀ ɛ rom ɓyɔ lɛ ɓyɛ ̀ kɛn ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓee ɗi ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi mɛgha ̀ y .
Ɓi Kiris a ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ i ̀ kum wu ɗyomzɛ ̀ n wu ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ wu riyi ɗi ɓiɓan wu ri wu ̀ nyamɛn .
Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ foŋi ̀ Pol , ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ lɔŋ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi ̀ nyi a ̀ kpaŋ a Atɛn , fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y min a Bere , Pol a ̀ romgi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ -Silas ɓɛɛ ̀ Timote jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , lɛ , ɓɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ tii ̀ nyi lɛ fyɛ ̀ ɗ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɔɔ kaka ̀ li ̀ lɔŋ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ lɛ : Kpana nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Nki ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuu Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , lɛ di mɓa mii ̀ ri ̀ ga ̀ ɓ .
Ɓɛ mɛ yag nyi ɓi wɛ ̀ y lɛ bwaɓ yi Man a ̀ jɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ , ri ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ nɗe ̀ resii saaɗ a ̀ nɛ mii ̀ ; ɓɛ nki keesii ɓi ɓyɛɓ ɓyaa a ̀ kpaŋ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓɛɛ risi ri ̀ wu .
Ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ri gɛn a ̀ ki ̀ ɓan a ̀ nɛ a ̀ rimi ; mɛ ̀ n ̀ kpaa fɔlɔɔ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kiris ri ̀ ki ̀ seŋi ki ̀ i ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ Sata ̀ n a kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ di ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ri ̀ Yeesus a Yorisalɛm , a ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ nyi ɓi fi ̀ ran fi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ kpaa nyi lɛ : I u ̀ yii lɛ u ̀ ri ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , lɛla fɛ , u kɛn ̀ ki ̀ ciɓi ̀ ɓi zi .
N ̀ kpaa mi ̀ ni kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ kpaa lɛ : n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say adɛŋ a ̀ cee ɓi masa ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ ; n ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom kɛ ̀ ɛ ki cee ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ romi nyi .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛraa a ̀ kpaga ̀ , nni Yeesus a ̀ nya ̀ mga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Elɔy , Elɔy , Lama saɓagtani , yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m Bɛ ̀ ll wɛ ̀ m , u ̀ rinii ɓa ̀ mɛ lɛ cɛ ?
Mum kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ lɛ i a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn , a kpaa lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll yɛɛ ̀ fe ̀ eghfee ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n mɛ ̀ . Ɓisuulɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ yin lɛ ki ̀ ɓe ki fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n nyi , nyimiɗ kɛ ̀ ɛ ki fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn mum .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ ɓɛ wooghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɔɔ cuu ̀ si ɓi ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓisuulɛ kidɛŋ ki ɓagha ̀ lɛ ki wɔg ki ki la ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ teri bimiɗ a ̀ nɗɛli kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ̀ ka ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , ki ɓa lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗii ɗi nyimiɗ a ̀ ki ren ɓi nɗem wii lɛ a ɓeŋ gɔ ̀ n yi ̀ i ̀ nkwɛ ̀ y , di a ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ syeesyee .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓi ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ɓi wuɓsɛɛ ba ̀ n i ̀ nɛ lɛ Sezare a ̀ Filiɓ ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɔ ɓi bee lɛ : Ɓum ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpaaghi ɓa ̀ lɛ mɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ghɛn ?
Ri ̀ kuu ɗi kiɓan aɗi ɗyɛɛ ghɛnɛɛ lɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ lɛ , jɛɛ Kan wɛ ̀ m a yu mɛ ̀ ja ̀ ŋbog ?
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɗi ti ɗi fuughi ̀ i ̀ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ŋwaa ̀ woogh ; nni ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛ ti ɓɛ woki ̀ , ki rii ̀ ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ i ̀ Kiris .
Nni ɓum lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ Yeesus .
N ̀ kpaa ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ lɛ ɓi wog n ̀ too ̀ ri ̀ ɗ . Fɔlɔɔ a re ̀ sii yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ mum a ̀ ɗyomzɛ ̀ n a ̀ yin ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n nsoo ̀ bog , a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓan ki ɓɛgeni wa ?
Ɓɛ tɔg nyi lɛ : Kali ɓi ̀ si n ̀ ko ̀ o u ̀ ri ̀ Me ̀ sii ! Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g ɓɔ lɛ : Nsoo ̀ ma ̀ a kpaa mi ̀ ni , ɓya ̀ a gherɛn ɓi .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ wɔwɔ ̀ la ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , ɓɛ ri ɓɛ ̀ ŋwaŋɛn mɛrɔ ̀ g lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ba ̀ li ̀ i ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ gherɛɛ Kan , lɛ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yiɓ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ baŋi ̀ i ̀ ɓɔɓɔ ̀ ka ̀ mɓɔɓɔghɛn .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ kpagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ ghaa ̀ gh di ɓɛɛ ̀ nyoonyolɛ ̀ n ɓɔri ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ .
kɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ɓɔg a Yorisalɛm a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ loka ̀ ki ̀ ɓaa ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ ni ̀ -fi ̀ tom ɓii ri mɛ ̀ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Araɓii fɔɔnnɛ n ̀ ki sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ti ̀ a Damas .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ mɛ kɛ ̀ rɛn syeesyee a ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ n lɛ ɓi ̀ si yɛɛ ̀ ɓɔɔɓɔgsi ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ti ̀ saa ̀ sa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi Yeesus Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m , tyɛ ̀ ki ki foŋ ntyweeyi wis ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki mɛmu ̀ u ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi kpaagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ɓi ̀ say ɓii lɛ : Ka ̀ ŋina mɛ ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ lɛ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ ri ̀ ɓya ̀ g , ɓi pig nyi ɓi biri ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓi dan , ja ̀ ŋ i ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ re ̀ eree ̀ dɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ŋaa ̀ ŋa ̀ a ̀ di ̀ min .
A ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓi fɔlɔɔ ɓi ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗii ɗi nyimiɗ , wɔ ̀ lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ nnyɛɛ ɓagha ̀ n ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ -ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓi be ̀ g i ̀ nɛ ̀ n nnɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ ki ̀ ɓan ki di ki kakay , lɛ Yeesus a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ wii ̀ ɓisuu kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Nni mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a fiɓɓɛn nyimiɗ di fɔɔnnɛ a ɗi bi ̀ rɛs , a ̀ nɔ ɓeŋ ,
Ki ɓagha ̀ ŋwosi jumɓa , di Saɓa ̀ t a ̀ ti lɛ a tumɛ ̀ n .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Pol a ̀ a ntɔɔgh lɛ ki ̀ ɓan kii kɛɛ ghaa ̀ gh yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza . Fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nkalii lɛ , ɓɛɛ ka ɓe ̀ ŋ nyi ɓi naa ̀ -za ̀ y a ̀ kpaŋ ŋwos anɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ romi ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza .
Ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ yii ɓi go ̀ n nsoo ̀ ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ ; nsoo ̀ ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ aɗyoo , nsoo ̀ Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ɓɔ a ̀ yii ɓi go ̀ n inɛ ̀ n , lɔŋ Ta ̀ a ̀ ta cɛ ̀ ncii yɛɛ yii .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di ɓaa kumi , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ kpila ̀ g ɓi mɛ ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛn ri ̀ ɓi fi ̀ ram fi lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ za ̀ y i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓiye ̀ g ri ̀ ɓi ɓeɓtɛn ɓi ɓi ti ɓi piki ̀ mum ɓi ri ̀ ɗyaŋ ri ̀ ɓi ri ̀ wu .
Mum a ̀ gagsi ̀ a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ gɛɓsɛ ̀ n di ɓum ɓɛ ri lɛɛ ̀ gwey , wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ lɔŋ cɛ ̀ ncii .
Nni ɓɛ yuyu ̀ gha ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roroɓ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ nɔŋza ̀ g ɓɔ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ kon ri ̀ ɓi ɓi ̀ ka ̀ ra ̀ lɛ , i Pyɛɛri a ̀ ti ɓii ̀ ghaghii , nsoo ̀ ci ̀ i ̀ ziŋ kii ki kom roa ̀ dɛŋ .
Ti ̀ tɔɔgh ɓumɓɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ki reɓ ɓɔ ɓi ɗii ɗi Kan Yeesus lɛ , ɓɛɛ say ɓi fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ ɗi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ɓɔmiɗ ɓɔ yɛɛ reni ki ̀ ɗi ̀ g mii ̀ .
