I ɓi keesii lɔŋ lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ keesii mi ̀ ni , ki ̀ ɓan ki kuurakɛn kaa ɓa ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkin , lɛ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ti ɓɛ keesa ̀ g girig ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ keesii ɓɔ .
Lɛ ɓi ̀ sii ̀ fe ̀ ki lɛ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ɓi ghɛnɛɛ lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ kɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ɓa lɛ , ri ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋ ɗi a ̀ ti a ̀ ɓe ̀ gi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pilat a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ , mɛ ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gtɔɔgh mii mɛ ghɛɓsii ɓi com , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ kɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛn asu n ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛnɛn , nni a ̀ teka ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , a ̀ so ̀ gtɛ ̀ n ɓya ̀ g ɓi mis mɛ gwi ̀ y i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ i ̀ ɓagha ̀ wɔɔ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : N ̀ -yin lɛ , n ̀ teɗ ki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɛ ki ɓi bwaɓ yi saaɗ a ̀ mum a ̀ nɛ , ki ̀ ɓan kii ki seesee lɔŋ mini .
Yiti ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ɓɛ ̀ la ̀ mi ̀ ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gɔmi ̀ na ̀ mɛ ̀ wog ; ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ki ̀ i com ki ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ̀ n ɓɛ tɔɔgh ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ki , ɓɛ ki fɛmɓɛn ɓi ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗi kiɓan kice ̀ m ki ki ri lɛ syeesyee .
Fɔɔnnɛ m ̀ pɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ zi ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ g ! Kan , ɓi cɛɓ kɛ ̀ m ki ̀ ce ̀ m , n ̀ ka foga ̀ ɓi com ki ki ri ki ̀ ce ̀ li ̀ , nsoo ̀ lɛ ki ki ri ki ̀ syeg ɓi ŋwɔm wɛ ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghesɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ sii ɓɔg ɓi fi ̀ tima ̀ , ɓɔɔ sugta ̀ g a ɓɛ ̀ mɛɛ ɓaa .
Ɓisuulɛ , fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ tɔɓ mɛ Kiris mɛ ti mɛ ghena ̀ g a lɔ ̀ ŋkis lɛɛ ̀ gwey , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ri ̀ fɔɔsi ̀ ɗi mɛrem mis ɗi ti ɗi ɓala ̀ g girig lɛɛ ̀ gwey lɛ Kiris .
Nni ɓɛ yugha ̀ y Yeesus ri ̀ ɗyaŋɗya ̀ ŋ a ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki nghay , a ̀ nce ̀ m ti ̀ mu ̀ m-mu ̀ m , Yeesus a ̀ ki wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ zi nyi ɓi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ lɛ , a ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ghɛnɛn .
N ̀ kpaa wɔ ̀ ɓi saaɗ a ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki u ̀ ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ ɓwɛɗ ki mum , wɔ ̀ ɔ nti u ̀ si ̀ na ̀ g ka ̀ nɗa wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ , u ̀ kɛ ̀ n ja ̀ ŋ inɛ u ̀ kɔ ̀ ni . Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , yɛ ̀ ɛ u ̀ ɓii ̀ ru ̀ ni , u ̀ ri na ̀ mgi ɓya ̀ g ɓyɔɔ , ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ yɛɛ sin ̀ wɔ ̀ ka ̀ nɗa , a ̀ ki kɛ ̀ n ɗi wɔ ̀ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ u ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓɛ minɛ ̀ n nyi , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ kaa ̀ ka ̀ rɛ ̀ nga ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ yi ghɛn anɛ ɓi ɓɔ yɛɛ cee ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog .
Lɛ ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n innɛ , nsoo ̀ Sara a ̀ ɓagha ̀ di a ̀ mɛ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a kiti boo i ̀ mum , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ tyweeya ̀ ka ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ roo ̀ zii nka ̀ g wii .
Nni com ki ɓum ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓoŋɓoŋ a ɓɛ ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi ̀ -ɓyom ki ri lɛ , ɓɛɛ resi lɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓum ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ tyweeyii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓɛ woka ̀ ɓito ̀ ki ̀ ɓin ̀ , nnɛ ɓɛ kɔri ̀ gha ̀ lɛ fyo ̀ oog , ɓɛ tumɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ kemzi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ nɛm girig ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ kuu mɛm ̀ bog bee inɛ lɛ , ɓɛɛ lɔɔ ̀ ghrɛn mɛ ̀ rem , di ɓɛɛ ɓa ri ̀ cɛɓ .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , ɓisuu nɗem wu nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓɛg wi ̀ s , n ̀ tɔɔgh mi ̀ ni lɛ ɓi funɛn mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ tuwe ki mum a ̀ ti a ̀ weeyi ̀ ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ; ɓi funɛn mi ̀ nii ̀ ɓɔmiɗ rifunɛ ̀ n ɗi ɗi ri cem , ɗyɔ ri ̀ tɛnɛn , ɗi ki ɓa ɗi ɗi rɔɔ Bɛ ̀ ll . Fɔlɔɔ yɛɛ ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ɓɔgsii Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ghɛɛna girig ti ̀ tima ̀ , nsoo ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ti teghaagh yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɓɔ ̀ , ti ti ti ɓala ̀ g lɛ , i coo bɛ ̀ ɓ kɛɛ ̀ tyɔtyɔg tyɔ , lɔŋ maa giya ̀ nnyɛɛ kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɛ ̀ si ̀ tyɔ ɓi ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a pupus tyɔ .
Nni a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi do ̀ n i ̀ ɓɛ ̀ o ̀ li ̀ vyee , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ yu nyi ki ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh a dwi ̀ ɗ lɛ : Kali ɓi ̀ si fin innɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ki ̀ lɛɛ , u ̀ ki fa ɓisi ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ki ɓi ri ̀ sugti ̀ i ̀ ɗyɔɔ , ri ̀ ri ̀ le ̀ g ɗi zi .
Ɓi ri ̀ keesi ̀ ɗi ti ̀ keesi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni , a ̀ a Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll nyi ri ̀ nyi innɛ ti ̀ ɓagha ̀ lɛ ti ̀ kɔ ̀ n lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni , ti ɓagha ̀ lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ ɓyɛɓ ɓis mii ̀ , lɛ ɓi ̀ ɓagha ̀ di ɓi ̀ ti ɓum ɓis ɓɛ nɗem lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ nɛn nnɛ ɓum ɓɛdɛŋ ɓɛ ɓi n ̀ ɗaŋ wu Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ ristɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ pɛsɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo , ɓɛ kpaa lɛ : Ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yin Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ kɛ ̀ raagh , ɓɛ ki ̀ ka ̀ ŋ ɓɔ lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓeŋ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓi Moyis .
Nni i ̀ pini ̀ gha ̀ ŋwɔm lɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ fengi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɗii ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ki ̀ nuugh ki Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi ɗyoo ɓiɗu ̀ m .
Fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mi ̀ ni ɓɔɔseŋi ɓɛ ̀ m ɓɛ nɗem , si ̀ i ̀ rɛɛna kɛ ̀ ɓi kpig , ɓi ̀ tɔɔtɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ntɔɔtɔyɛn ɓi ki ̀ say ki Kan , ɓi ̀ ki yi lɛ , ki ̀ say ki ɓi ki ̀ ki nyi kaa wu ɓi zɛy .
Gheeghe ̀ ŋzɛɛna ri ̀ tɛ ̀ g ɗi mɛtɛ ̀ g mɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ mɔ , di fɔɔnnɛ ɓi roo ̀ zi ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki Kiris .
I ŋwaa ̀ woogh di ɓɛɛ ̀ kakali ki ̀ ɓan ki kilɔ ̀ ŋ ki aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓ kɛ ̀ ɛ yi com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ : Ghe ̀ ghey a ̀ mum a ̀ yu ̀ ki ̀ pisii boo i ̀ nɛ ɓaa mi ̀ si ɓi nɗem wu ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n ; ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ boo i ̀ nɛ i ̀ kpi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi bee aɗyoo .
Nsoo ̀ fɔlɔɔ , mum a ̀ ghɛɛsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi lɛ a ɓuŋ nyi fɛlɛ lɛ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ɓi mɛ ̀ ree ̀ mɛ ɓum lɛ ɓɛ riri ̀ si ̀ gha ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n .
Fɔɔnnɛ Yeesus a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓi ja ̀ ŋ ɗii lɛ Gɛsemane , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : Kɔ ̀ riina fɛ , mɛ ̀ n ̀ ka kɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ŋzaagh fɛnii .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ a Zyeriko , a ̀ sya ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ ba ̀ n .
lɛ Zyaŋ a ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓti ̀ gha ̀ ɓum ɗi ̀ mɛ ̀ nig , ki ̀ ɓan kifog mi ̀ nii ri ɓii ̀ ɓa ̀ ɓtɛɛ ri Ki ̀ tɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay di ɓɔɔ mɛru ɓɛ ghaghii .
Yeesus a ̀ yigha ̀ lɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ ɓɛɛ tɔg nyi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ; fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ lɛ : Ɓi tɔɔtɔɔ ̀ ghrɛ ̀ n azi anɛ ɓi ki ̀ ɓan ki ma ̀ a kpaa mi ̀ ni lɛ , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n lɛsa ̀ g ɓya ̀ a ghɛɛ ̀ di ɓi mɛ , nni yɛ ̀ ɛ maa ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaghii ti ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ̀ di ̀ mɛ ̀ .
A ̀ loogh ki ̀ kpaa lɛ wɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ kɔ ̀ ni ɓi nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na , nsoo ̀ mɛ ̀ fafa ̀ a ̀ mɛ zɛy , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ tuwe ɓi ɓɛ tɔni lɛ ɓɛɛ ɓɔgsi wɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɓyɔ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ɓɛ funɛɛ ɓisuu zo ̀ ghɛ ̀ n i ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe , ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi rɔɔ ɓi wɔ , kɔlɛ ɓi ̀ fu ̀ na ɓi ̀ n ɓyɛɛ ̀ ki ̀ ikilɛ ̀ n lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ i Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ rɔ ̀ ɓka ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ke ̀ ŋi ɓum ɓɛ titom ɓɛ ɓɛ kigha ̀ ki ̀ ɓe , a ̀ ra ̀ m lɔŋ a ̀ ɓangi ̀ ɓɔ , a ̀ ki pi ̀ ki ɓɔ ɓi bɛŋ yi yi ri ri ̀ biri ̀ m , wɔɔ nnɛ ɓɛ kaka ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɓanɛn ɓɛ ɓoŋɓoŋ ɓɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ m ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll ;
Nni ɓi ɗi lɛ ɓi yi lɛ , Man a ̀ mum a ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ n ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓe fɛ ɓi ziinɛ , Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ki ̀ sɛkɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ kin ̀ lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u teɗ kon wɔɔ ̀ u sug a mɛɛ mɔɔ .
Tyɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ tɛɛna Bɛ ̀ ll ja ̀ ŋbog fɔɔnnɛ nyi girig a ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u ja ̀ ŋbog , so ̀ ona ɓya ̀ g ɓin ɓyɛɛ tɛn , mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe , ɓi ̀ ki kpɔg mɛrem min , mi ̀ ni ɓum ɓɛ tyoo tiɓɛɛ ̀ .
Ya ̀ a ɓa ti ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ bee inɛ n ̀ ɗenga ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓaa ɓɛ ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn , ŋwos anɛ m ̀ ɓanga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ca ̀ g lɛ nkpaŋzii ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ki Egiɓtɛn . Ɓɛ ɓega ̀ ɓi bee inɛ n ̀ ɗenga ̀ i ̀ nɛn ri ̀ ɓɔ , fɔɔnnɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ ghɛ ̀ righa ̀ ɓi girig nɗem aɗyoo ri ̀ ɓɔ , ri ̀ kpaa ɗi Kan ɗyɛɛ ̀ ɗi ̀ n .
Ɓɛ ri do ̀ o ̀ yi Isirayɛl , ɓɔɔ ̀ ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ghaasi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɔn ɓii , a ̀ fa ɓɔ ri ̀ kem ; ri ̀ ɓɔ nnɛ a ̀ renga ̀ bee yii ̀ , a ̀ fa ɓɔ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna , a ̀ re ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ki fa ɓɔ mɛ ̀ ka ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛkɛ ̀ ghi ̀ gha ̀ fyem fi nyɔn di ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ u ̀ teɗ kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ nɛ ̀ n , u ̀ ɓɛki ̀ ɓɛ ̀ si ̀ tam ̀ ɓɛ mii ̀ , ɓisuulɛ ɓɛ wola ̀ wɔ ̀ , u ̀ ki kwe ̀ ɗ ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ to ̀ ki ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓisuu Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ bwaɓ yɔɔ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ tyo ̀ ŋdɛ ̀ nga ̀ y ɓɔ a nyoo , a ̀ n ̀ yɛ ̀ ŋ ɓɔ , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛɛna aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , kɛ ̀ ɓi risi .
Nɗomii ̀ mi ̀ ni nyi ri ̀ azi lɛ , ɓi yi ri ̀ ɓa ɗis , a ̀ ki fɔɔsi mini mɛ ̀ rem .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ ghɛŋi ̀ gha ̀ min bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ɓɔɔ ̀ gh ɓi ki ̀ te ki lɛ si ̀ kɔ ̀ mɔɔr lɛ di fɔɔnnɛ a ghɛn ̀ Yeesus a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ fyee ɓi ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ̀ n .
