Wɔ ̀ lɛ guŋgum nyii ghɛɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ rɛɛ ri ri ̀ sɛɛ ̀ di ̀ ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dii nyi , ɓisuulɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ghaghii yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ̀ sa ̀ ma ̀ ki caaɓi .
A ̀ pisigha ̀ sɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ m ̀ ɓeɓɛn a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ɓisi ɓi nyoo innɛ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi mii ̀ ɓi nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si ; a ̀ pisi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ si nyi yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kpanga ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ɓi ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ki ̀ ghɛɓsaagh ɓɛgeni ɓin ɓɛ ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ yeeyee ̀ si ̀ ɓɔ , ɓi ̀ ki yi ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓ ɗi ɓɛ ̀ ke ̀ n lɛ syeesyee .
Nni wɔɔ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y nnɛ a ̀ ɓegsi ̀ gha ̀ mis , di ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗyɛɛ ̀ pye ̀ npyen nyi mis , a ̀ ghɛn yi ̀ lɔŋ Abiraham fi ̀ ra ̀ ɓ , ɓɛɛ ̀ Lazaari n ̀ kɔ ̀ kɔriyɛn nyi ɓi n ̀ wɔŋi ̀ .
Nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g i ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ masa ̀ anɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say wii ̀ , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ cenɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi pon wii ̀ , a ̀ ca ̀ ɗ nyi lɛ a kɛn ̀ .
Ɓisuulɛ mum n ̀ ce ̀ m a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a kamɛ ̀ n ri ̀ cɛɓ kii , a ̀ ri ̀ kɔ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii , wɔ ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗimzii cɛɓ kii ɓisu wɛ ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓisuu Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ , nnyɛɛ ri kɔ ɓii ̀ ghɛɓsii .
A ̀ tumɛ ̀ n ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kin ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓɛ ghaaghra ̀ ka ̀ , ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ti nyi .
Kɔ ̀ ri ɗyomzɛ ̀ n u ̀ ki si ̀ i ̀ rag righerɛ ̀ n ɗi ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ u ̀ kaka ri ̀ yɔ ̀ , ga ̀ ɓ i ̀ ɓum i ̀ nɛ ̀ n yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ja ̀ ŋbog ɗi ̀ ri ̀ wu , ɓisuulɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ nghɛɛ lɛ mɛ ̀ ki ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ mɔɔ mɛ ɓiisɛɛ ɓi kirɔɔtɛɛ ɓi mis mɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ri ̀ fa ɗi nɗem ɗi ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , ɗi ri ri ̀ wu , ri ̀ fa ɗi nɗem ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Nghay , ɗi ri cɛɓ ri ̀ fyo ̀ oog .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ ̀ zyaa ̀ zyaa ɓɛ ɓɛ kpanga ̀ n ̀ ɗaŋ ɗi nyi , ɓɛ sɛɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ mgi ̀ gha ̀ girig nyi .
N ̀ ki yii lɛ nko ̀ o ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ri nyoo yi ̀ i ̀ gi yɔ ̀ , nko ̀ o a ̀ ɓagha ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ yɔ ̀ , Bɛ ̀ ll yɛ ̀ ɛ yii , mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yii ɓi .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ woka ̀ mɛ ̀ nyi ̀ inyi ̀ g lɛ di Yeesus Kiris a resi ri ̀ ni ̀ ɗ ɗii ɗi nɗem ɓi mɛ ̀ fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe a ̀ n ̀ tonto , fɔɔnnɛ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ki ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ ki ̀ re ̀ mzɛna ̀ ɓisuu ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓii ̀ gherɛɛ nyi lɛ ɓɛɛ teɗ cɛɓ ki fiɗya ̀ ɓ fikɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛnga ̀ lɛ ri ̀ Pyɛɛri ri ̀ Zyaŋ di ɓɛɛ ̀ kɛ ̀ nkɛn lɛ ɓɛɛ ɗiŋi ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ lɔnga ̀ ɓɔ mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni .
Yeesus a ̀ a nti a ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɓum ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll . Nni ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛgwey , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g-ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ mɛ ̀ fo ̀ m mɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ kaaka ̀ a ̀ gha ̀ bee inɛ ɓɛɛ wey nyi .
Ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ ɓis , nsoo ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ girig wusi ̀ nɛ ̀ ɗ lɛ cɛɓ ki ti ̀ ghɛɓka ̀ ri ̀ mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ki ɓagha ̀ ki ̀ tɛnɛn , kɔ ti ̀ lɛ saaɗ , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kifenɛn mii ̀ .
N ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ kali ̀ lɛ , a ̀ ri ̀ nyi ɓii ̀ faa ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ a ɓeŋ i ̀ kum wii wuce ̀ m .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɔɔ kpaagha ̀ ɓɔ ki ̀ ɓan ki kaa ki ̀ i ɓɔ ɓi bee inɛ a Emayus , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓaa re ̀ mii Yeesus di a ̀ mɛ ɓɛg bi ̀ rɛs .
Mi ̀ ni ɓɛ ̀ geni ɓɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ seŋi ɓɛ ̀ m , ɓigomi ̀ nɛ ramina mɛ ̀ ree ̀ , ɓi wog com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ n ̀ ɗe ̀ si ̀ mi ̀ ni .
Nni ɓi ̀ ghɛɛ ! Ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ a tɔ ̀ kɛɛ mɛ ̀ , a ɗiɗi fɛ n ̀ ɗaŋ ri mɛ ̀ .
Giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ɓagha ̀ ri ̀ ɗyem , a ̀ ki kuukugsɛ ̀ n lɛ ɗyem ɗi kiki ̀ gha ̀ nyi a ̀ wowo ̀ g ri ̀ kɛŋ ɗi giɓ a woki ɓi ri ̀ yay .
Nni ri ̀ fo ̀ m ɗi lɛ Eroodɛ ɗi woka ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ kem ɗi Yeesus ɗi ɓagha ̀ di ɗi ti ɓii ̀ pa ̀ pasi ɓum ja ̀ ŋ bimiɗ , ɓɛ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ lɛ , Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis yɛɛ ghemɓɛɛ yi ̀ a nyɔ ̀ ɛ ̀ y , kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ri ̀ mii ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ki ̀ kiyɛn da ̀ m .
Ki ̀ ɓan ki asu ki ri lɛ : Ɓaana ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ nɛ kɛ ̀ ɛ lɔ ̀ gtɛn ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n , lɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ti a ̀ lɔki ̀ n ̀ kun wu ɓiɓe .
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ kɛnga ̀ ki ̀ kpaŋi ̀ a Kapɛrinawum , yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi naa , nni a ̀ tɔka ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g lɛ : Cɛ ɓya ̀ a nyoonyo ̀ lɛ ̀ n mii ̀ bee bimiɗ ?
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓyom ɓi ̀ n ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ ɓi woŋzakɛn , ɓɛ ̀ pi ̀ rɛɛti ̀ rɛ ̀ ɓɛɛ nti ɓɛ ɗiŋɗa ̀ g ɓɛ ̀ ŋwos ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ki ̀ den ki asu lɛ ɓɛɛ ki ki ̀ say kaa .
I ŋwaa ̀ to ̀ ogh Man a ̀ mum ki ̀ ɓe , ɓɛ cenɛ ̀ n nyi , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ŋwaa ̀ nɛ a ̀ ɓii ̀ to ̀ ogh Kitɛntɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ n ki Nghay ki ̀ ɓe nsoo ̀ ɓi cɛɓ ki gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , nsoo ̀ ɓi cɛɓ ki ki rii ̀ , ɓaa cenɛn ɓi nyi ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ .
ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛnghɛn kirɔɔ ɓi ziinɛ , ɓɛ ɓa yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ghɛɛ ɓi kirɔɔ , ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ziinɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ seesee ̀ rɛ ̀ n ɗi mii ̀ ɗyaa finɛn ti ɓi ̀ .
Ri ̀ ɓa ɗi lɛ ŋwaa ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ kɛ ̀ rɛn nsoo ̀ lɛ a ̀ yin nkɛ ̀ rɛn ɗi yin com , ki ̀ ɓan ki ki ri bimiɗ a ̀ com ki ri lɛ mum a ɓa nyɔɔnyɔn a ̀ mum .
A ̀ kpaagha ̀ fɔlɔɔ lɛ kɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ kali ̀ gha ̀ lɛ : Mɛ ̀ ɛ nɗimzii ɓi nsoo ̀ ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓumɓɛ u ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ lɛ n ̀ ghagsi ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɗyɛm ̀ a ̀ tumɛɛ gɛɛ ̀ nɛ , a ̀ kpaŋ ri ̀ duri ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛɓɛɛ ̀ , ɓisuulɛ n ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan a ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛɛ ɓi ki wii ̀ ja ̀ ŋ idɛŋ , lɔŋ a Yorisalɛm .
Fɔɔnnɛ fyo ̀ oog a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ ɓum ɓɛ yin ɗi i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wulɛ ɓɛ wog , a ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi mɛrem min ri ̀ mɛ ̀ yiti ̀ min ɓi Yeesus Kiris ɓi ɗu ̀ m .
A ̀ gherɛ ̀ nga ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ pwa ̀ a ̀ , a ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , a ̀ kpaa lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin Kiris .
a ̀ a lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ yu ̀ ɗii ɗyɔ ri ̀ ɗyɔ , ki ̀ ɓan kifog ri ̀ fɔɔsi ̀ ɗi ɓi ̀ i nfɔɔsii nyi n ̀ ɗem ɗi nfɔɔsii girig ɓi ̀ si mɛ ̀ rem ; a ̀ a nkalii ɓi ̀ si coo za ̀ y i ̀ nɛ ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ yɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ghɛn ̀ mɛ ̀ , ri ̀ mɛ ̀ kɛɛgh min , ri ̀ ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi ɓi ̀ ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ falɛn a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi nki ̀ i lɛ mɓii ̀ sɛn ti ̀ ki ̀ woo ̀ gh ki ̀ nya ̀ a ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey .
I i ̀ ko ̀ o ̀ waa ri ̀ lɛ wu kpaa lɛ : Yɛ ̀ ɛ mɛ ̀ n ̀ -yin ca ̀ g , n ̀ -yin kika ̀ ɓ ki nyoo , fɔlɔɔ a yin lɛ a ̀ re ̀ g wɔ lɛ wɛɛ ɓa lɔŋ kika ̀ ɓ ki nyo ̀ o ̀ .
A ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree yɛ ̀ ɛ rifo ̀ m , a ̀ kpaa ɗyɔ lɛ : Nkɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ u fa mɛ ̀ nto wu Zyaŋ Ba ̀ ɓtis ɓi taasa ̀ lɔŋ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ min ɓɛyila ̀ g ɓɛ kin ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ rɛn lɛ : Mi ̀ nii kɔni ɓi lɛ ɓi ghaa ̀ rag girig ?
Ri ̀ kpaa ɗi lɛ a ̀ ɓɔka ̀ ɗi resii cɛ ? Ɗi resii lɛ a ̀ sɛnga ̀ ɓi ki ̀ rimi ki zi .
Ɓɛ ̀ yali ̀ ɓɛ Yeesus ɓɛ n ̀ ti ɓɛ kɛngi ̀ ki ̀ ɗii ̀ Paska ̀ a Yorisalɛm be ̀ g yi ̀ ce ̀ m .
Bɛ ̀ ll a teɗ ri ̀ kem ɓi ri ̀ fa ɗii ɗi ɗi ri kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ gh .
Fɔɔnnɛ coo kila ̀ a ̀ ki ̀ ki ɓagha ̀ ɓi naa ̀ -Bɛ ̀ ll , ki lani ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ̀ la ̀ na ̀ ɓiɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n yi ̀ aɗyo ̀ o ̀ , a ̀ kpaŋ azi ; zi i nyɛ ̀ ŋɗɛ ̀ n , mɛ ̀ ɓan mɛ lanla ̀ n .
lɛ di ɓi ɗi lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ mɛ mɛfo ̀ m , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ̀ te ̀ ete ̀ ɗ ɓi ɓum , ri ̀ mɛ zo ̀ m yi kimbɛ ̀ rɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi zo ̀ m yin ̀ aɗyoo , ri ̀ mɛ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m lɛ , ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpa ̀ n ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yin ɓɛkpa ̀ n , ri ̀ ɓɔɓti ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ mɛn .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ mɛ re ̀ si ɓisi lannɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ ki ̀ la ̀ g lɛ ti ɓa lɛ saaɗ ɓi mis mii , kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ; kaa ̀ ta ̀ a ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ri ̀ ɓɛ ̀ kpaŋzi ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓɛ ɓuga ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kin ̀ ;
Nyaasi soŋi ɓɛɛ ̀ gaa , a ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ki n ̀ tonto ki n ̀ ka ̀ g wu rii ̀ mii ̀ wu ̀ foŋɛn .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ ! Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɛm ̀ , n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi ri mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ti ri ̀ N ̀ ghay a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , wɔ ̀ lɛ n ̀ to ̀ o ̀ ghrɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ ri mi ̀ ni yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓumɓɛ ɓi mɛ ̀ mu ̀ u ̀ , lɔŋ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ kaka ɓɔn ɓɛsa ̀ g ɓi Kiris .
Nni ɓɛ tɔka ̀ Yeesus lɛ : U ̀ woogh com ki ɓɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ ? Yeesus a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ! mi ̀ nii ka ɓala ̀ ɓi yɛ ̀ ɛ ki ri ki ̀ ka ̀ nɛn lɛ : U ̀ teka ̀ ri ̀ kem ɓi ŋwɔm wu ɓɔɓti ɓɛsa ̀ g , ri a ɓɔn ɓɛ ɓɛ kaka ɓi mɛli ̀ ?
Nni giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ yu ̀ gha ̀ y girig ɓi ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n kɔm ̀ kin ̀ , a ̀ tum ri ̀ fa ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll ri ̀ kem , a ̀ ki kpaakpaa ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m ɓɛ ɓɛ ɓoŋɓo ̀ ŋga ̀ go ̀ ri i ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll ɓisuu Yorisalɛm ki ̀ ɓan ki Yeesus .
I ti ̀ ki ̀ gha ̀ fɔlɔɔ , ki yin lɛ ti ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ɓi lɛ ti ̀ tɔg mi ̀ ni n ̀ ghɛɓsɛn , ti ̀ kɔ ̀ nga ̀ lɔŋ yɛɛri lɛ ti fa mi ̀ ni ki ̀ fe ̀ e ̀ ghrɛna ̀ ki ɓi ̀ ri ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ .
Ɓi gba ̀ a ̀ yi ajɛ ̀ m , Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ca ̀ ɗka ̀ lɛ ɓi ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ nɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ti ̀ bee yi ɓi kɔni lɛ ɓyɛɛ nɔɔ ̀ ti .
Nni a ̀ kɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ ɗiŋii kisa ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kin ̀ ; roa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ rom nyi lɛ a kɛn ̀ nyi ki ̀ ɓe ̀ ŋi je ̀ e ̀ a dɛm .
Ɓisuulɛ ki ̀ ɓan kice ̀ m ki Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ki ̀ i ki pisɛ ̀ n ki ̀ ye ̀ g ki kiɓan , ɓi ri ̀ ghɛn ɗi ɓum , ki cee ɗyomzɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓum , ki ɓɛ ghɛɛ i ̀ kɔ ̀ g wu Bɛ ̀ ll mii ̀ , ki cee i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ɓum .
Pyɛɛri a ̀ Kpaa min nyi lɛ : Mɛ ̀ n-yin ɗi mɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ni nsoo ̀ gol lɔŋ com ki n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɔ kɛɛ ̀ ki n ̀ faa wɔ ̀ : Ɓi ɗii ɗi Yeesus Kiris a ̀ nɛ a Nazarɛt pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo u kɛɛ ̀ ghi !
Ɓisuulɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ri ̀ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wulɛ nkɛn ̀ a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ yii cɛɓ ri ̀ a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ ɓɛ ka yi ɓi cɛɓ , a ɓɛ ̀ yii ̀ -ɓi ̀ ɓan , ri ̀ a ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ yii ɓi com .
Ɓɔɔsoŋ ̀ , n ̀ kalii mi ̀ ni lɛ , ɓi konag ri ̀ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛɛ ̀ syo ̀ ŋsyoŋ yi gasɛ ̀ n , ɓɛ ki kɛ ̀ ɛkɛɓti ̀ ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n ti ̀ ɓa ̀ g , ri ̀ ki ̀ ɗin ̀ ɗyɛɛ ̀ yooyogsi ̀ ri ̀ re ̀ sa ̀ g ɗi ɓi ̀ teka ̀ . Kɛ ̀ ɓi ɓasɛn ɗi mɛ ̀ kuu mɛ ɓum mɛ ̀ n .
Yeesus a ̀ ɓe ̀ n , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ kpaa ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n lɛ : Sugha a ɓum ɓɔɔ , u kali ɓɔ com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki Kan a ̀ a ki ̀ i ɓisu wɔɔ , ri ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ a ̀ a woogh wɔ ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ Pol a ̀ kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ a ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ fɔlɔɔ , nni Fɛstus a ̀ kpaagha ̀ jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pol , u ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g , coo riyi ɗyɔɔ ɗi ɓiɓan ɗi ghaasii wɔ ̀ ki ̀ ye ̀ g .
Kan lɛ : Bee inɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ reni ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ nɛ lɛ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔ , ajɛ ̀ m i ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ fɛlɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ foŋi ̀ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛm ̀ ɓi mɛ ̀ rem maa , n ̀ ka ̀ n ɓɔ ɓyɔ ɓi nto . A ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓ min lɛ :
Wɔ ̀ lɛ ɓi ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓin ̀ ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m , ɓaana ri ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n . N ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ ri ̀ com ki ki ti ki raɗki ̀ ɓum syeesyee a ̀ ri ̀ ra ̀ ɗ .
ɓi ri ̀ falɛ ̀ n ɗi ɓi ri ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ɓi ̀ ɓɔ ̀ ɓtɛ ̀ nti ̀ ki ̀ rɔɔrɛɛ ki ɓi ri ̀ geni ; ɓi ki ̀ rɔɔrɛɛ ki ɓi ri ̀ geni ki ̀ n , ɓi ̀ foŋ ̀ di ̀ n ̀ kɔ ̀ nɛ ̀ n .
Nni n ̀ kɔmɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ̀ suja ̀ a ̀ a ̀ nɛn a ̀ teka ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛn , a ̀ kɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ yɔ ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ kɔ ̀ mɛ ̀ n a ̀ gwey a ̀ kali ̀ nyi lɛ : Ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ki lɛ Pol , kɛ yaa regii mɛ ̀ , ki kpaa lɛ n ̀ -yuy ri ̀ dɛli ̀ i ̀ nɛ a lɔ ̀ ŋkɔɔ , ɓisuulɛ i ̀ ri ̀ ri ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kidɛŋ ki yɛ ̀ ɛ kpaa ̀ wɔ ̀ .
A ̀ re ̀ mzi ̀ gha ̀ girig ɓi ̀ si ri ̀ si ̀ tam ̀ wi ̀ i ̀ , a ̀ foŋ ɓi ̀ si ɓi ̀ ɗu ̀ n ɓi Nghay ɓi mɛ ̀ rem , ɓi ɓi resii lɛ , ti ̀ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ ɓi ̀ rɔɔ ɓi a ̀ nyamga ̀ ɓisu wis .
fɔlɔɔ nnɛ ɓi ̀ ɓii ̀ ki ̀ i lɛ ɓi ̀ ɗi , ɓi ̀ ki nɔ ɓi ki ̀ kpana ̀ kɛm ̀ ɓi ki ̀ lɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ , ɓi ̀ ki kɔ ̀ ri ɓi mɛ ̀ kɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ mɛ rila ̀ mi ̀ , lɛ ɓi yɔm ̀ mɛ ̀ pwi ̀ ɗ n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ mɛɓɛɛ ̀ mɛ a Isirayɛl .
Ɓɛ nsɛɛgh geesɛ ̀ n yɔ ̀ ɔ ̀ ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓi Ki ̀ seŋi ki Kiris . Ki ri ɓii ̀ ɓaa ̀ lɛ syeesyee di u ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ ɓɔ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ ki ri lɛ ki rɔɔ Bɛ ̀ ll .
Ɓisuulɛ ri ̀ ɓa ɗi ̀ ce ̀ m ɗi Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ ri ̀ ɗi yugha ̀ ki ̀ kɔ ̀ rii ɓi nyoo i ̀ Kiris lɛ kɔɔ ̀ kɔɔ ̀ .
Ɓi ɓɛg a ̀ nɛ a ɓum ɓɛ zɛy ɓɛ ɓɛ ti ɓɛ ̀ gherɛ ̀ n , ti ̀ ka ̀ nga ̀ ɓɔ ɓi ̀ ɓan ɓi ti ̀ renga ̀ lɛ , ɓɛɛ celi ɓyɛn ɓi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ ɓɛ woli ɓi ri ̀ ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗi ɓinu ̀ n ɓi zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , ɓɛ celi ̀ ti ̀ bwaɓ yi nya ̀ m i ̀ nɛ i ̀ wii lɛ swi ̀ i ̀ ɗ , ri ̀ ti ̀ sɔ ̀ mɔ ̀ g .
Fɔɔnnɛ a ̀ laŋmɛ ̀ nga ̀ lɛ a tɛg wɔɔ ɓi ɗu ̀ m , a ̀ ghɛn ɓɛ ̀ ɓanɗas ɓɛ ̀ nɔ ̀ nɔŋiyɛn , wɔ ̀ lɛ a ̀ ɗiŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi zɔ ̀ ŋ .
Ɓi ti ̀ ca ̀ ɓ ti Paska ̀ ti ̀ ce ̀ m , gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ a n ̀ ti a ̀ ca ̀ ɗki ̀ ki ̀ mbu ̀ ŋ ki ̀ fog , ki ɓum ɓɛ kilɔ ̀ ŋ ɓɛ tɔɔgh lɛ , a caɗ .
Nni a ̀ sugti ̀ gha ̀ y ja ̀ ŋ inɛ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓɛ ɓagha ̀ , a ̀ tanɛ ̀ n ɓɔ di ɓaa cuu tilo ̀ , a ̀ kpaa Pyɛɛri lɛ : Simɔn , u ̀ lali yɛɛ lɔɔ lɛ ri ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ ɗi ̀ lɛ u kɔri cem bimiɗ a ̀ hawo ̀ ɗyaa yaagh wɔ ̀ wa ?
Fɔɔnnɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓi gwi ̀ y i ̀ nɛn ɓɛ ruru ̀ mi ̀ gha ̀ lɛɛ ̀ gwey ɓi ki ̀ ɓan kii . Ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛdɛŋ lɛ : A ̀ ri ̀ syeesyee a ̀ mum ; ɓɛ ̀ ro ɓɛmbog lɛ : A ̀ g ! A na ̀ anaa ̀ zi ̀ gi ̀ kɔm ̀ ɓum bee .
Ɓaana ri ̀ mɛ ̀ wog ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m wi ̀ n ɓisuu rini ̀ ŋ ɗi ɓi ̀ ti ɓi ̀ ni ̀ gi ̀ Kiris .
ki ̀ ɓan kifog Ɓɛ ̀ yudɛ ̀ n ɓɛ ɓen ̀ lɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ ca ̀ ɗ mɛ , fɔlɔɔ nnɛ mɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ ɗi ̀ n ̀ tiniyɛn lɛ nghagsii ̀ ki ̀ ɓan kɛm ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Kaaza . N ̀ ki yin ri ̀ fe ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ , n ̀ sɔmɛn ɓumɓɛ ɓi kilɔ ̀ ŋ kɛm ̀ .
Ki ̀ ɓan kifog , n ̀ -yii lɛ nsoo ̀ ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , com ki ̀ ce ̀ m ki u ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ tɔɔ ̀ gh Bɛ ̀ ll , a ̀ ri ̀ wɔ ̀ kɔ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ .
Ɓi ɗi yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ dɔ ̀ gsɛna ɓyɛɛ ̀ kpaakpa ̀ a ̀ , ɓɛ ti ɓɛ sogha ̀ g ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ri ̀ bwaɓ , nsoo ̀ ɓi ̀ ɓe , ɓi ti ɓi ɓala ̀ g ɓi ̀ cenɛn di bwaɓ yi kpaŋi .
Ɓɔɔ ɓɔn ɓɛ ̀ m , siito ̀ n a ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ti lɛ ! Fɛlɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ɓi ̀ woka ̀ lɛ ŋwaa ̀ dɛŋ a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ri ̀ ɓii ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ɗuu ri Kiris a ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u yi , ɓɛ ̀ ɗu ̀ u ̀ ri ̀ Kiris ɓɛ mɛ te ̀ ghɛn ɓigomi ̀ nɛ , kɛɛ resii ɓi ̀ si lɛ siito ̀ n a ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n yɛɛ ti lɛ .
lɛ a yɔm ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ren ki ̀ ɓan kaa , lɛ di ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓum ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓyɛɛ teɗ n ̀ cɛ ̀ m ɓisuu ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓiɓan ɓi ɓɛ kigha ̀ , ri ̀ ɓi ntoo ̀ te ̀ ɗ wu ɓɛ resi ̀ gha ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll , ri ̀ ɓisuu ɓiɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓi ɓɛ ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ ɓe ɓɛ ɓɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ risi Bɛ ̀ ll ɓɛn ̀ ɓɛ kpaa ̀ kpa ̀ ŋzi ̀ gha ̀ di ɓɛɛ ̀ feefengi ̀ nyi .
Sata ̀ n yɛɛ ri seŋi wi ̀ n fɔɔnnɛ ɓi kɔ ̀ nkɔn lɛ di ɓya ̀ a ki ̀ i ri ̀ kɔ ̀ n ɗi seŋi wi ̀ n . A ɓalag n ̀ woli ̀ -ɓum a ̀ tumɛ ̀ n a ri ̀ tumɛ ̀ n , a ̀ ki ka rɛli ̀ gha ̀ ɓi ɓi saaɗ nsoo ̀ ŋwos bog , ɓisuulɛ , saaɗ a maa ̀ ɓa ɓi a lɔ ̀ ŋkii ; ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki a pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ɓum , lɔŋ com ki ki rii ̀ nyi ɓi nɗem kɛɛ ̀ ki a kpaakpaa ɓɔ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ pwaa ̀ , a ̀ ki ɓa ti seŋi ɓɛ ̀ pwa ̀ a ̀ .
Gɔmi ̀ na ̀ a ̀ tɔgti ̀ lɛ : Ki ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ki kiɓan aɗi kɛɛ ̀ ki a ̀ ki ̀ i ? Ɓɛ syaadi ̀ ti ̀ ri ̀ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ lɛ : Ɓɛɛ kpan ̀ nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Mum a ̀ fagha ̀ ɓi ɓisi ɓi ̀ ɗila ̀ g ɓi ti ɗi zɛy , ti ̀ sasa ̀ la ̀ lɔŋ lɛ ri ̀ i ̀ ru ri ̀ ŋwos , ti ̀ wowo ̀ g mɛ ̀ tɔɓ ri ̀ ki ̀ fɔli lɛ n ̀ tɛ ̀ g wis wɛ ̀ kɛɛ ̀ siŋ wa ̀ a ̀ dɛŋ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
Wɔ ̀ lɛ Yeesus a ̀ mi ̀ nɛ ̀ n giɓ anɛ ̀ n ; ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii ɓɛ tyoŋdɛ ̀ n nyi a nyoo , ɓɛ kpaa nyi lɛ : Na ̀ ɓa giɓ anɛ , ɓisuulɛ a nɔ ̀ ɔnɔɔ ̀ ti ̀ i ̀ ɓi ̀ si ajɛ ̀ m ri ̀ ki ̀ yoo ̀ yo ̀ o ̀ .
Maata a ̀ ɓa ̀ g lɛ : Ɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ Kan ! n ̀ gherɛɛ lɛ wɔ ̀ yɛɛ ri Kiris , Man a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ nɛ a ̀ ghɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ ki ̀ yu ̀ u ɓi ziinɛ .
Gi ̀ n mɛ ̀ yɛɛ sɛri ̀ gha ̀ nya yɛ ̀ ɛ n ̀ sɛɛ ̀ dɛ ̀ nga ̀ mɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ ɓi zi lɛ mɓɔgsi mi ̀ ni , ca ̀ a ̀ mɛ ̀ n ki n ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ mi ̀ ni Syeesyee a ̀ Ɓɔlɛ a ̀ Bɛ ̀ ll zɛy ri ̀ zɛy , kɛ ̀ ɓi ko ̀ o ̀ sɛn ?
A kɔ ̀ nga ̀ girig lɛ a resi le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ ri ̀ kem ɗii ɗi teghɛɛ ɓi san a ̀ nɛ a ɓɛ ̀ roɓɛ a ̀ ti a ̀ woki ̀ nyi ̀ ighnyi ̀ g , ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ a ̀ loka ̀ ki ̀ pe ̀ gsɛɛ abɛ ̀ y lɛ ɓɛ ɓii ̀ teri ̀ ri ̀ kem ɗi ̀ i ̀ .
Ɓi ̀ ɓeɓta ̀ g ɓi ɓɛfe ̀ g ɓi mum ɓi nɗem , ɓi ti lɛ i ɓi teri ɗyem , ɓi yay ki ̀ ɓe ; ki ̀ ɓe ki ɓala ̀ g lɛ i kaa te ̀ ɗ , ki yay ri ̀ wu .
Ki ̀ kɔm ki ɓagha ̀ di ki mɛ ra ̀ ɓsɛn ri be ̀ n i ̀ ri ̀ ɓa ̀ y ga ̀ ɓ , ɓikus ɓi riɓa ̀ y ɓi yee ̀ ye ̀ e ̀ si ̀ kɔ , ɓisuulɛ bɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ susu ̀ ka ̀ y ɓɔ ɓi nyo ̀ o ̀ .
lɛ di ɓyom ɓi ̀ ce ̀ m ɓi ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ aɗyoo , ri ̀ ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ ɓi ziinɛ , ri ̀ ɓi ɓyɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛɓ ɓi zi ɓiɗu ̀ m , ɓyɛɛ ɓag mɛ ̀ ɗu ɓi zi , ɓi ɓɔgsi ̀ ɗii ɗi Yeesus ,
Nni a ̀ kpaagha ̀ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n jɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ aɗyoo lɛ : Pɛ ̀ sɛn aɗyoo , u rɛli mɛrɛy wɛ ̀ ɛmiɗ . Fɔɔnnɛ ŋwaa ̀ nɛ ̀ n a ̀ pɛ ̀ sɛ ̀ nga ̀ aɗyoo lɛ fa ̀ tweɗ , a ̀ ghagsɛ ̀ n ɗi ̀ ri ̀ kɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ .
Nni ki ̀ bog ki ɓi ɓɔ ki kɛnga ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ree , ki ̀ nɔg dɛ ̀ ɓ ɓi ɓi ̀ kpaakpam ɓi mɛrɔ ̀ g , ki ɓam ̀ dɛ ̀ ɓ i ̀ nɛ ̀ n ɓi ki ̀ syo ̀ ŋ ki nam ̀ Yeesus lɛ a nɔ , di kɛɛ ̀ kpaakpaa lɛ : Ca ̀ rina ti ghɛn ̀ n ̀ koo ̀ Eli a ̀ ɓii ̀ yu ̀ u lɛ a kɔsi nyi ɓi kɔrɔs .
Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ : N ̀ ɗi ̀ ɓii ̀ faa ̀ n ̀ tyweeyi wɛm ̀ ɗi ̀ nyi . Ri ̀ ti ̀ lɛ : Ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ri ̀ ɓɔn ɓɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ fagha ̀ mɛ ̀ , ɓi ̀ si ɓɛɛ ̀ ɓɛ lɛ ̀ .
Fɔɔnnɛ giɓ anɛ ̀ n a ̀ ghɛŋi ̀ gha ̀ ɓi-reɓ , wɔɔnnɛ ja ̀ ŋ inɛ Bɛ ̀ ll a ̀ pe ̀ gsɛ ̀ nga ̀ nyi i ̀ ɓagha ̀ , lɛ a ̀ ri ̀ wɔɔ ɓii ̀ ɗiɗii a ̀ kpaŋ mɛ ̀ ru tɔɔsi ̀ m ɓɛ ̀ hɔnɗɛ ̀ ɗ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ ri ̀ mɛ ̀ ru mɛ ̀ tin mɛraa .
Nni Yeesus a ̀ kɔ ̀ ri ̀ gha ̀ ɓi zi , a ̀ reŋi ̀ ɓɛ ̀ yila ̀ g ɓii n ̀ tɛ ̀ ɗ ri ̀ ɓɛɓɛɛ ̀ , a ̀ kpaa ɓɔ lɛ : I mum a ̀ kɔ ̀ ni lɛ a ̀ ɓa n ̀ ɗɛ ̀ li ̀ -asu ̀ , a terɛn nyimiɗ yɛ ̀ ɛ siito ̀ n a ̀ mum ɓi nyi ̀ inyi ̀ m a ̀ ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m , a ̀ ki ɓa n ̀ ki ̀ i ̀ -ki ̀ say a ɓum ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m .
Yɛ ̀ ɛ ti ̀ ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ŋwii ɓɛraa wɔɔ , nni ti ̀ ɓɔka ̀ fi ̀ tima ̀ fidɛŋ fi a Alɛgsaŋdirii , fi fi ghagsi ̀ gha ̀ bu ̀ ma ̀ wɔɔ ɓi ki ̀ ri ̀ ŋ ki riɓa ̀ y kin ̀ . Fi ̀ tima ̀ fin ̀ fi ɓagha ̀ ɗii lɛ , bɛ ̀ ll yi rifas .
Ɓi ̀ yii lɛ ɓumɓɛ ɓɛ ri ɓi nlog a ̀ mɛ ̀ ree ɓi nlɛmɓog wu tica ̀ ɓ ɓɛɛ ̀ ghɛghɛŋi ɓɛsɛ ̀ ɛ ̀ ɓɛ ̀ ce ̀ m wɔ ̀ lɛ lɔŋ mum bog yɛɛ ti a ̀ kpagi ̀ , bee ̀ bɛ ̀ y a ̀ teɗ mɛ ̀ raa ̀ mɛ ɓi nlog a ̀ nɛ ̀ n ? Nni ghɛŋiina le ̀ g a ̀ nɛ lɛ ɓi teɗ mɛ ̀ raa ̀ mɛ ɓi nlog .
Ɓɛ ̀ fa ̀ ri ̀ zyɛŋ ri ̀ Ɓɛ ̀ sa ̀ du ̀ syɛŋ ɓɛ yugha ̀ y yɛ ̀ ɛ Yeesus lɛ ɓɛɛ fee ̀ ghrɛn nyi . Fɔɔnnɛ ɓɛ tɔka ̀ nyi lɛ , a ki da ̀ m i ̀ nɛ yɛ ̀ ɛ resi ɓɔ lɛ i ̀ te ̀ ɗ wii wu rii ̀ yɛ ̀ ɛ Bɛ ̀ ll .
